 car...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/18.mp3","time_start":39.5,"time_end":43.19},{"position":19,"content":"What size is the engine?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/19.mp3","time_start":43.19,"time_end":45.09},{"position":20,"content":"It's 1200 ccs.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/20.mp3","time_start":45.09,"time_end":46.99},{"position":21,"content":"Thank you...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/21.mp3","time_start":46.99,"time_end":48.18},{"position":22,"content":"and the make and model?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/22.mp3","time_start":48.55,"time_end":50.71},{"position":23,"content":"It's a Hewton Sable.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/23.mp3","time_start":50.71,"time_end":52.71},{"position":24,"content":"Could you spell the model name please?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/24.mp3","time_start":53.35,"time_end":56.19},{"position":25,"content":"Yes... SABLE.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/25.mp3","time_start":56.19,"time_end":60.24},{"position":26,"content":"Ah yes... thanks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/26.mp3","time_start":60.75,"time_end":63.15},{"position":27,"content":"And when was it made?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-7-test-2-part-1-2023-07-28-17-12-17/27.